        *
 
Suppose someone writes something bad about "Narasimha" and supp=
ose I am offended when I read it, thinking "I" am being criticized. Here I =
may have a mental object called "Narasimha", whom I may see as being attack=
ed when I read that mail, though nothing is being done to any physical body=
. My self-identification with this mental object (i.e. thinking that "I am"=
