at mental object and using it as an instrument of experiencing, I may somet=
imes experience happiness (e.g. when someone writes great things about "Nar=
asimha") and sometimes experience sadness (e.g. when someone writes bad thi=
ngs about "Narasimha"). As long as I do that, I am bound.
 
